OL,3,CFuture of town's heritage trams under
OL,4,Cthreat
OL,6,FHeritage trams have been running along
OL,7,Fthe Blackpool seafront for 140 years,
OL,8,Fbut their future is up for debate as
OL,9,Fthe building that houses some of the
OL,10,Ftrams needs major renovation.
OL,12,FTramtown is the workshop where several
OL,13,Fof the heritage trams are kept, along
OL,14,Fwith all the machinery that is needed
OL,15,Ffor their maintenance.
