OL,6,FThe building dates back to the 1920s
OL,7,Fand it is also a popular visitor
OL,8,Fattraction, but Tramtown has been
OL,9,Fforced to close temporarily due to
OL,10,Felectrical problems. It is the latest
OL,11,Fin several issues around the workshop.
OL,13,FLeader of Blackpool Council,
OL,14,FCouncillor Lynn Williams said: "Four
OL,15,Fyears ago was the first time the
OL,16,Fpossibility of demolition was raised
OL,17,Fbecause of the condition and the cost
OL,18,Fof maintaining the building, but we
OL,19,Fcontinue to work with tramtown and we
OL,20,Fare supporting their funding bid"
