OL,3,CFuture of town's heritage trams under
OL,4,Cthreat
OL,6,FThe Council estimate it will cost up
OL,7,Fto #3 million to refurbish the
OL,8,Fworkshop and they would prefer
OL,9,Finvestment in the nearby tramshed.
OL,11,FThere are currently 2 heritage trams
OL,12,Frunning through Blackpool
OL,13,Filluminations with around 40 trams
OL,14,Fbeing held in the tramshed.
OL,16,FBlackpool Council wants to get funding
OL,17,Fto improve the tramshed, while
OL,18,Fvolunteers at Tramtown want any
OL,19,Finvestment to be spent on the current
OL,20,Fworkshop.
