OL,6,FThe volunteers insist the original
OL,7,Fengineering equipment like the forge
OL,8,Fand wheel lathe cannot be moved from
OL,9,Fthe workshop due to their age, but the
OL,10,Fmachinery is vital to keep the
OL,11,Fhistorical trams running.
OL,13,FCouncillor Paul Galley is the
OL,14,Fvolunteer coordinator at Tramtown, he
OL,15,Fexplains the difficult job of
OL,16,Fmaintaining the historic trams:
