OL,6,FCarol Martin is a volunteer at
OL,7,FTramtown and was a conductor on the
OL,8,Ffamous boat tram for years, she has
OL,9,Ffond memories of working on the trams:
OL,11,F"To be a conductor on an open top tram
OL,12,Fone of the boats in the summer, we
OL,13,Fwent up and down, up and down all day
OL,14,Flong for 8 hours , the tram was full
OL,15,Fof people, happy people, it didn't
OL,16,Fmatter if it was rainy or sunny they
OL,17,Fwere just happy"
