OL,3,CFuture of town's heritage trams under
OL,4,Cthreat
OL,6,FHoward Parish spent 43 years working
OL,7,Fat Tramtown repairing the heritage
OL,8,Ftrams, he said he "loved renovating
OL,9,Fand looking after the trams" but that
OL,10,F"it constantly get harder to maintain
OL,11,Fthe trams because you can't go to the
OL,12,Fshops to buy the parts you have to
OL,13,Fmake them"
OL,15,FHoward says: "It is essential that the
OL,16,Ftrams stay, they are a part of
OL,17,FBlackpool, like the Tower and the
OL,18,Fdonkeys"
